<div class='questionText'>
<div class='spoiler'>
<a class="spoiler" href="/questions/730940-who-will-cry-when-you-die-interesting">This question contains spoilers...</a>
<span class='spoilerAnswerText'>
<a class="jsShowSpoiler spoilerAction">(view spoiler)</a><span class="spoilerContainer" style="display: none">[Who will cry when you die ? Interesting, as a poser. Question is: Does it matter whether or not anyone does ? For you wouldn't know either way, would you ? If anyone cried or felt relieved at your going. And, would you care ? <a class="jsHideSpoiler spoilerAction">(hide spoiler)</a>]</span>
</span>
</div>
